title: Wiz Khalifa - Taylor Allderdice mixtape
description:
Taylor Allderdice is the tenth mixtape by American rapper Wiz Khalifa, released for free on March 13, 2012. The name of the 17-track mixtape is the same as the high school that Wiz Khalifa attended.
